```puml
@startuml Gestion_Absences_Sequence_Absence
title Flux de Gestion des Absences - Diagramme de Séquence

actor Professeur
participant "API" as API
participant "AbsenceController" as Controller
participant "AbsenceService" as Service
participant "Repository" as Repo
participant "NotificationService" as NotifService
participant "Database" as DB
actor Étudiant

Professeur ->> API: POST /api/absences/bulk
Note over API: { classId: 1, studentIds: [...], date: "2024-04-20" }
activate API

API ->> Controller: MarkBulkAbsences(BulkDto)
activate Controller

Controller ->> Service: MarkBulkAbsences(BulkDto)
activate Service

loop Pour chaque StudentId
    Service ->> Repo: GetStudent(studentId)
    activate Repo
    Repo ->> DB: SELECT FROM Students WHERE Id = @id
    activate DB
    DB -->> Repo: Student
    deactivate DB
    Repo -->> Service: Student
    deactivate Repo
    
    Service ->> Repo: CreateAbsence(Absence)
    activate Repo
    Repo ->> DB: INSERT INTO Absences
    activate DB
    DB -->> Repo: OK + AbsenceId
    deactivate DB
    Repo -->> Service: Absence
    deactivate Repo
    
    Service ->> NotifService: SendNotification(studentId, message)
    activate NotifService
    NotifService ->> Repo: SaveNotification(Notification)
    activate Repo
    Repo ->> DB: INSERT INTO Notifications
    activate DB
    DB -->> Repo: OK
    deactivate DB
    Repo -->> NotifService: OK
    deactivate Repo
    NotifService -->> Service: OK
    deactivate NotifService
end

Service -->> Controller: List<AbsenceResponse>
deactivate Service

Controller -->> API: 201 Created
deactivate Controller

API -->> Professeur: { markedCount: 4, absences: [...] }
deactivate API

Note over Étudiant: Étudiant reçoit notification

Étudiant ->> API: GET /api/notifications
activate API
API ->> Controller: GetNotifications(studentId)
activate Controller
Controller ->> Repo: GetNotificationsByUserId(studentId)
activate Repo
Repo ->> DB: SELECT * FROM Notifications WHERE UserId = @userId
activate DB
DB -->> Repo: Notifications
deactivate DB
Repo -->> Controller: Notifications
deactivate Repo
Controller -->> API: Notifications
deactivate Controller
API -->> Étudiant: 200 OK + Notifications
deactivate API

Étudiant ->> API: GET /api/absences/my
activate API
API ->> Controller: GetMyAbsences(userId)
activate Controller
Controller ->> Repo: GetAbsencesByStudent(studentId)
activate Repo
Repo ->> DB: SELECT * FROM Absences WHERE StudentId = @studentId
activate DB
DB -->> Repo: Absences
deactivate DB
Repo -->> Controller: Absences
deactivate Repo
Controller -->> API: AbsenceList
deactivate Controller
API -->> Étudiant: 200 OK + Absences
deactivate API

@enduml
```
